Rogue Scientist
The Rogue Scientist is an independent researcher who refuses Coalition control
in the pursuit of knowledge. They explore the ruins of the pre-Rifts world,
catalogue alien life forms, and study dimensional phenomena.

Rogue Scientists begin with multiple languages, advanced mathematics, and a
broad scientific base. They choose from Science, Technical, Medical, and Lore
categories. They are not combat-focused but are invaluable in the field.

Attribute requirements: IQ 12.
Starting equipment: Portable laboratory kit, specimen containers, laptop
computer, data library, concealed sidearm, and field clothing.
